WEBVTT

00:00:36.283 --> 00:00:37.909
Your attention, please!

00:00:37.909 --> 00:00:41.455
Make your way directly across
the courtyard to the main barracks.

00:00:41.455 --> 00:00:44.374
Leave all your cell phones
and cameras here.

00:00:44.374 --> 00:00:48.420
I repeat, cell phones
and cameras are not allowed inside.

00:00:48.420 --> 00:00:50.547
Leave any cell phones and cameras here.

00:00:50.547 --> 00:00:52.006
Helen!

00:00:53.258 --> 00:00:54.718
Can we bring her up?

